comment: LaVine (MIN) makes contact with Oladipo's (ORL) arm during his side to side arm movement prior to the ball hitting LaVine's leg.
Oladipo (ORL) cleanly strips the ball from Wiggins (MIN).
Wiggins (MIN) legally contests Harris' (ORL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact is considered incidental.
Payton (ORL) and Rubio (MIN) make incidental contact with one another while going after the loose ball.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with Dieng's (MIN) body that affects his shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on LaVine (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Garnett (MIN) and Rubio (MIN) make incidental contact with Payton (ORL) that does not affect his RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Gordon (ORL) clamps Wiggins' (MIN) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Dieng (MIN) makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Oladipo (ORL) fails to maintain legal guarding position on the slip play prior to the contact with Wiggins (MIN).
Prince (MIN) commits a take foul on Nicholson (ORL).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Nicholson (ORL) was the FT shooter, was confirmed.
Gordon (ORL) cleanly blocks Wiggins' (MIN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the block is considered incidental.
